#: ../../toolchain/moon/script-mode.md:1
msgid "Running `.mbtx` Scripts"
msgstr "运行 `.mbtx` 脚本"

#: ../../toolchain/moon/script-mode.md:3
msgid ""
"The Moon build system lets you write script files in MoonBit without any "
"module or package configuration files. Script files use the special "
"`.mbtx` extension."
msgstr ""
"Moon 构建系统支持直接编写 MoonBit 脚本，无需模块或包配置文件。脚本文件使用 `.mbtx` 扩展名。"

#: ../../toolchain/moon/script-mode.md:6
msgid "Run a `.mbtx` file"
msgstr "运行 `.mbtx` 文件"

#: ../../toolchain/moon/script-mode.md:8
msgid "Write a script `script.mbtx`:"
msgstr "编写脚本 `script.mbtx`："

#: ../../toolchain/moon/script-mode.md:10
msgid ""
"///|\n"
"import {\n"
"  \"moonbitlang/core/list\" @ls\n"
"}\n"
"\n"
"///|\n"
"async fn main {\n"
"  let xs = @ls.from_array([\"1\", \"2\", \"3\"])\n"
"  debug(xs)\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""
"///|\n"
"import {\n"
"  \"moonbitlang/core/list\" @ls\n"
"}\n"
"\n"
"///|\n"
"async fn main {\n"
"  let xs = @ls.from_array([\"1\", \"2\", \"3\"])\n"
"  debug(xs)\n"
"}\n"

#: ../../toolchain/moon/script-mode.md:23
msgid "Then run this script directly:"
msgstr "然后直接运行该脚本："

#: ../../toolchain/moon/script-mode.md:25
msgid "moon run script.mbtx\n"
msgstr "moon run script.mbtx\n"

#: ../../toolchain/moon/script-mode.md:29
msgid ""
"In `.mbtx`, you can declare imports at the top of the file using the same"
" syntax as package configuration. There is one difference: import paths "
"can optionally include a version `@version` after the module name:"
msgstr ""
"在 `.mbtx` 中，你可以在文件顶部声明导入，语法与包配置相同。不同之处在于：导入路径可以在模块名后可选地"
"包含版本 `@version`："

#: ../../toolchain/moon/script-mode.md:33
msgid ""
"///|\n"
"import {\n"
"  \"moonbitlang/async@0.16.5/fs\",\n"
"  \"moonbitlang/async@0.16.5\",\n"
"}\n"
"\n"
"///|\n"
"async fn main {\n"
"  ...\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""
"///|\n"
"import {\n"
"  \"moonbitlang/async@0.16.5/fs\",\n"
"  \"moonbitlang/async@0.16.5\",\n"
"}\n"
"\n"
"///|\n"
"async fn main {\n"
"  ...\n"
"}\n"

#: ../../toolchain/moon/script-mode.md:46
msgid "All imported packages from the same module must use the same version."
msgstr "来自同一模块的所有导入包必须使用相同版本。"

#: ../../toolchain/moon/script-mode.md:48
msgid ""
"If the import path is not explicitly versioned, it uses the latest "
"version in the local registry index."
msgstr "如果导入路径没有显式指定版本，则会使用本地索引中的最新版本。"

#: ../../toolchain/moon/script-mode.md:52
msgid "Run a `.mbtx` script from stdin"
msgstr "从 stdin 运行 `.mbtx` 脚本"

#: ../../toolchain/moon/script-mode.md:54
msgid "Moon supports running a `.mbtx` script from stdin:"
msgstr "Moon 支持从 stdin 运行 `.mbtx` 脚本："

#: ../../toolchain/moon/script-mode.md:56
msgid "cat script.mbtx | moon run -\n"
msgstr "cat script.mbtx | moon run -\n"

#: ../../toolchain/moon/script-mode.md:60
msgid "You can also use a heredoc, a feature provided by the shell:"
msgstr "你也可以使用 heredoc（由 shell 提供的一项功能）："

#: ../../toolchain/moon/script-mode.md:62
msgid ""
"moon run - <<EOF\n"
"fn main {\n"
"  println(\"hello\")\n"
"}\n"
"EOF\n"
msgstr ""
"moon run - <<EOF\n"
"fn main {\n"
"  println(\"hello\")\n"
"}\n"
"EOF\n"
